---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-elysium-dark uppercase tracking-widest">
        About
      </h3>
      <div class="flex-grow h-px bg-elysium-dark/10"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="pl-0 md:pl-8 border-l-0 md:border-l border-elysium-dark/20">
      <p class="text-lg text-elysium-text leading-relaxed font-medium mb-4">
        
      </p>
      <p class="text-md text-elysium-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        I am an AI developer and software engineer specializing in systems engineering and computational infrastructure. I work on projects ranging from full-stack application development and process optimization to advanced bioinformatics solutions.
        <br><br>
        
        I have directed engineering teams to deliver centralized management systems for non-profits and built scalable Python-LLM analytics pipelines that drastically cut review times for multinational tech platforms. Alongside technical development, I have also shaped institutional standards by authoring comprehensive policies on the ethical use of Generative AI.
        <br><br>
        
        Lately, I have been diving deeper into AI-driven bioinformatics, specifically leveraging protein language models for generative design. I treat this complex infrastructure as a continuous sandbox, where my daily structure prioritizes rhythm over intensity, and every friction point is captured as training data to compound long-term results.
      </p>
      
      <a 
        href="/assets/resume.pdf" 
        target="_blank" 
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 border border-elysium-dark text-elysium-dark font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase hover:bg-elysium-dark hover:text-elysium-light transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        <span>Inspect Full Resume</span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>